These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, cherry
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, action
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, ambient
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person watching action movies##1
2. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
6. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | juice      | lemonade |
| Food          | cherry      | broccoli       |
| Hobby         | gardening | magic-tricks  |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | action      |
| Music-Genre   | country       | ambient      |
| Sport         | weightlifting    | golf       |

