.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pear, peas
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, dancing
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, analyst
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, reggae
2 different pets are kept: lizard, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter
1. the manager is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
2. the analyst is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating pear##1
5. the manager is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
6. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food          | pear | peas |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | dancing  |
| Job           | manager      | analyst  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | salsa      |
| Pet           | lizard     | snake    |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | helicopter     |

