2. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
3. the fan of jazz is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
5. the firefighter is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
6. the person eating raspberry is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |         2          |
| Beverage      | 7up          | almond-milk               |
| Food          | radish       | raspberry           |
| Hobby         | board-games       | skydiving            |
| Job           | firefighter | pilot |
| Music-Genre   | d&b         | jazz            |
| Transport     | roller   | jet-ski               |

 